article.description: Drey Mingo had 13 points and Sam Ostarello scored 12 to lead No. 14 Purdue to a 59-45 win over Bowling Green Monday night.
article.headline:
Drey Mingo scores 13, Sam 
Ostarello adds 12 for Purdue
article.linkText: Mingo sends No. 14 Purdue past Bowling Green
article.story:
WEST LAFAYETTE, Ind. --  Drey Mingo had 13 points and Sam Ostarello scored 12 to lead No. 14 Purdue to a 59-45 win over Bowling Green Monday night.

Mingo and Ostarello also had 12 rebounds each for the Boilermakers (3-0), with Ostarello blocking four shots. Chantel Poston also scored 12 points for Purdue, which led 25-18 at halftime.

Danielle Havel had nine points to lead the Falcons (2-1). Bowling Green shot just 28 percent (14 of 51) from the field.
